info.senderName: NWS Duluth (Northeast Minnesota and Northern Wisconsin)
info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued June 28 at 7:27PM CDT until June 29 at 8:00AM CDT by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM CDT THURSDAY... * WHAT...Visibility one half mile or less in dense fog. * WHERE...Carlton and South St. Louis Counties. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Fond du Lac Band. * WHEN...Until 8 AM CDT Thursday. * IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The densest fog is ongoing and expected to continue overnight tonight on the top of the hill in and near Duluth and westward into Carlton and South St. Louis Counties.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
